Prohibited steps order

[Name] must not

remove the child[ren] from the care of [name] or any person or institution (including any nursery or school) to whom that party has entrusted the child[ren]’s care, nor instruct or encourage anybody else to do so, other than for the purpose of contact agreed in writing or ordered by the court, in which case the child[ren] must be returned promptly at the end of each such contact period;

allow the child[ren] to live at a different address than [address];

remove the child[ren] from their current school;

remove the child[ren] from the United Kingdom;

allow the child[ren] to be known by a different surname than [surname];

